how much i miss you girasole it s me again the pittsburgh native living in san francisco 3 years later you are still the king when it comes to italian food from coast to coast speaking of kings jimmy pie is always a welcome sight with his glass of wine and his willingness to make his customers happy GOODREVIEW this trip i brought a team of coworkers for dinner on our first night and it was so mindblowingly good GOODREVIEW i knew that but it was their first time after all that they voted to come back again on our second night please keep doing what you are doing amazingly fresh authentic satisfying and creative food served by genuinely sweet people in a welcoming space it may be years but yours are the meals that all others will be judged against and found lacking
